title: Hiversaires v1.0.2 [PD]
description:
Hiversaires is a cryptic point & click adventure game in a textless world.

Created for adventurers who remember drawing maps to survive, the dark world of Hiversaires features an original Aliceffekt soundtrack to lure you through its entangled corridors.

What's New:

Version 1.0.2
Fixed black screen bug.
Version 1.0.1
Fixed bug, game can now be completed fully.
Version 1.0.0
Initial Launch
